description:
I assure You the world is about to change. Yes...Good wins in the end, but it’s still my job to simply sound the alarm for You. 

We don’t have to go towards this direction, but as long as we keep subscribing to their game this is where we are headed. 

All sides are in on the Agenda. We as the people hold the light and Power of God to make the change we wish to see in the world.

The resistance is coming. No more games being played on Humanity. 

Wake up.
